/cal_data.discript: GET=> Returns events in a json format based on the parameters passed in. Time is in hhmm format. Date is in yyyymmdd format
/cal_data.format: RETURNED=> [{Date : #, Start_Time : #, End_Time : #, What : '', Where : '', Group_GP : #},{...}]

/create_account.discript: POST=> Creates a new account. Takes an email, hashed password, name, current year (1-5, 5 is staff), student leader status, and gender.
/create_account.params: PARAMS=> (email : '', hashPass : '', name : '', year : #, isStudentLeader : bool, gender : '', isAdmin : bool)
/create_account.format: RETURNED=> 403 error if an account already exists with the given email

/delete_account [WIP].discript: DELETE=> Deletes an existing account. Takes an email and a hashed password.

/login [WIP].discript: GET=> Takes an email and a hashed password. Returns a 403 error if the login was not successful.

/orders.discript: GET=> Endpoint used for testing purposes only. Contact Wyatt to have this set up for your own testing.
